<div class='relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-950 via-emerald-800 to-emerald-600 text-white'>
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'>
    <div class='absolute -top-32 -left-24 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/30 blur-3xl'></div>
    <div class='absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-lime-300/20 blur-3xl'></div>
    <div class='absolute top-1/3 right-1/5 h-40 w-40 rotate-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 blur-xl'></div>
  </div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16'>
    <header class='mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center'>
      <h1 class='mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-4xl'>
        目的に合わせて
        <span class='block text-lime-200'>最適なモードを選択</span>
      </h1>
      <div class='mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-100/90'>
        <p>牌効率を鍛えたい、終盤の判断を磨きたいなど、目的に合わせてモードを選べます。</p>
        <p>進みたいトレーニングを見つけたら、ゲームを開始しましょう。</p>
      </div>
      <div class='mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-100/80'>
        <span class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2'>
          <span class='text-emerald-200'>モード数</span>
          <span class='text-base font-bold text-white'><%= @game_modes.size %></span>
        </span>
        <% mode_type_labels = { 'final_round' => 'オーラス特化', 'match' => '対局形式' } %>
        <% @game_modes.map(&:mode_type).uniq.sort.each do |mode_type| %>
          <span class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2'>
            <span class='h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lime-300'></span>
            <%= mode_type_labels[mode_type] || mode_type.to_s.humanize %>
          </span>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class='mt-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-8 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur'>
      <div class='flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-emerald-100/80'>
        <span class='font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-200'>Select Mode</span>
      </div>

      <div class='mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3'>
        <%= render partial: 'game_mode_card', collection: @game_modes %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
